GIT awesomeness
===============

seed is a subtree and can be pulled in when modified.
The steps were:

git remote add origin https://github.com/polsene/2d_game.git
git pull origin master

git remote add seed https://github.com/cs0rbagomba/seed.git
git fetch seed
git merge -s ours --no-commit seed/master
git read-tree -m -u seed/master
git commit -m "Imported seed as a subtree."

and now:
git pull -s subtree seed master
